#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:2
msgid "Script Initialization List"
msgstr "脚本初始化列表"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:4
msgid ""
"Types can be registered to allow them to be created from initialization "
"lists."
msgstr "可以注册类型以允许从初始化列表创建它们。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:7
msgid "List Factories and Constructors"
msgstr "列表工厂和构造函数"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:9
msgid ""
"Similar to normal factories and constructors, the list factories for "
"reference types and list constructors for value types can be registered by "
"``.list_factory`` and ``.list_constructor``, respectively."
msgstr ""
"与普通工厂和构造函数类似，引用类型的列表工厂和值类型的列表构造函数可以分别通"
"过 ``.list_factory`` 和 ``.list_constructor`` 注册。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:12
msgid ""
"If you already have wrapper functions, you can register them by "
"``.list_factory_function`` or ``.list_constructor_function``"
msgstr ""
"如果你已经有包装函数，可以通过 ``.list_factory_function`` 或 "
"``.list_constructor_function`` 注册它们"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:14
msgid ""
"This kind of helper needs you to provide the pattern of the initialization "
"list, such as ``float, float`` or ``repeat int``. For helpers using the "
"constructors of C++ class directly, you can also specify the optional "
"template parameter ``ElementType`` for the element type of initialization "
"list. If the list pattern contains ``repeat`` or ``?`` that need to parse "
"manually, you can just use the default template parameter, which is ``void``."
msgstr ""
"这类辅助工具需要你提供初始化列表的模式，例如 ``float, float`` 或 ``repeat "
"int``。对于直接使用 C++ 类构造函数的辅助工具，你还可以为初始化列表的元素类型"
"指定可选的模板参数 ``ElementType``。如果列表模式包含需要手动解析的 "
"``repeat`` 或 ``?``，你可以直接使用默认模板参数，即 ``void``。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:19
msgid ""
"The helpers expect the constructors or wrapper functions use a pointer "
"(``ElementType*``) to receive the buffer of initialization list. The "
"requirements about return value and other parameters are the same as normal "
"factories and constructors, which is described in :doc:`how to register an "
"object type <../object_type>`."
msgstr ""
"这些辅助工具期望构造函数或包装函数使用指针（``ElementType*``）来接收初始化列"
"表的缓冲区。关于返回值和其它参数的要求与普通工厂和构造函数相同，详见 :doc:`如"
"何注册对象类型 <../object_type>`。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:52
msgid ""
"Unlike C++, each type in AngelScript can only have **one** list factory or "
"constructor."
msgstr ""
"与 C++ 不同，AngelScript 中的每种类型只能有**一个**列表工厂或构造函数。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:54
msgid ""
"For repeated pattern, asbind20 provides a helper class to parse it from a "
"raw ``void*``."
msgstr "对于重复模式，asbind20 提供了一个辅助类来从原始 ``void*`` 解析它。"

