msgstr "初始化列表策略"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:63
msgid ""
"The asbind20 provides some policies for adapting existing C++ paradigm for "
"constructing from a range of value."
msgstr ""
"asbind20 提供了一些策略用于适配现有的 C++ 构造模式，以便从值的范围进行构造。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/init_list.rst:65
msgid ""
"Policies are passed via ``use_policy``, which accepts one or more policy "
"types:"
msgstr "策略通过 ``use_policy`` 传递，它接受一个或多个策略类型："

